marking ingredient requirements:
mark an element with class "quantityDependant". it will be blue and display an amount and a unit depending on the chosen recipe quantity
this element requires an id, with format
id="f(amount)u(unit)"
where (amount) is a number and (unit) is a unit symbol. both without parentheses. additionally, a plural form of the unit can be added with - and the ending of the plural form. with -! the following will be the whole plural unit. 